{"tid":1202103,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你會唔會理隔離家事？其他人理你家事又幫到咩？","createTime":"2019-06-11T07:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T07:57:58.000Z","uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7251974f6947d2a9c54f67341031422c077d0bb8","tid":1202103,"uid":216899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"喺唔同社交媒體 都見到有人話等台灣美國英國歐盟發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想講唔好再咁大期望 港共連103萬上街都唔聽 點會理外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n就算有用都係得少少影響 唔好放錯重點 咁睇重其他人有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n香港人 靠自己啦 希望大家會出現野餐 守護自己家園<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班狗官搞完香港就可以拍屎忽走 我地仲要喺留喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係有用嘅資訊發放點 歡迎巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/antielabhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fantielabhk&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAoyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=8652e436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/antielabhk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/protectourplace\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fprotectourplace&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAoyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=0d172bc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/protectourplace</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/reminder612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Freminder612&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAoyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=1fa08e2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/reminder612</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/103team/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F103team%2F&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAoyL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=bd884d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ht